---
title: Honey-Sesame Chicken Bowl with Asian-Style Slaw & Rapid Peanut Rice
description: Inject your night with a burst of flavour by combining sesame seed-topped chicken with nutty basmati rice. Top this baby off with an Asian-style slaw and a dollop of soy mayo for a dish that’ll have you salivating long before you plate up.
